.SH "SYNOPSIS"
Here you will find a list of all the available topics for help related to \fBDalma\fR and how to call for help
.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Users can request help on any specific topic using the following command:
.
.P
\fBman dalma\-<topic>\fR
.
.SS "where \'topic\' can be one of:"
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
storage \fI\.\./html/dalma\-storage\.html\fR : Display information about the different filesystems and how to use them
